      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $\\mathcal{C}$ le cercle : $x^2+y^2=1$. Soit $M$ un point de $\\mathcal{C}$ d'angle\n    polaire $\\theta$ et $D_\\theta$ la droite passant par $M$ d'angle polaire\n    $2\\theta$. Trouver l'enveloppe des droites $D_\\theta$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{C}\\)</span> le cercle : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x^2+y^2=1\\)</span>. Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(M\\)</span> un point de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{C}\\)</span> d’angle polaire <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\theta\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(D_\\theta\\)</span> la droite passant par <span class=\"math inline\">\\(M\\)</span> d’angle polaire <span class=\"math inline\">\\(2\\theta\\)</span>. Trouver l’enveloppe des droites <span class=\"math inline\">\\(D_\\theta\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "1727bea4-df6f-4bd0-bc25-e02a1c8b3b48",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$x=\\frac{3\\cos\\theta-\\cos3\\theta}4$,\n\t     $y=\\frac{3\\sin\\theta-\\sin3\\theta}4$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(x=\\frac{3\\cos\\theta-\\cos3\\theta}4\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(y=\\frac{3\\sin\\theta-\\sin3\\theta}4\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
